div.p: FUSE kernel module manages multiple outstanding requests using unique IDs. myfs can serve concurrent syscalls from ls, cat, and cp simultaneously using worker threads.

g.text: + getattr(path: const char*, st: struct stat*): int + open(path: const char*, fi: fuse_file_info*): int + read(path: const char*, buf: char*, size: size_t, off: off_t): int + write(path: const char*, buf: const char*, size: size_t, off: off_t): int
